WEBVTT
Kind: captions
Language: en

00:00:40.685 --> 00:00:41.602
- Take one.

00:18:37.020 --> 00:18:39.030
- The problem is enormous.

00:18:39.030 --> 00:18:42.180
Sprawling favelas are
controlled by drug gangs

00:18:42.180 --> 00:18:44.130
and shootouts occur every day.

00:19:16.440 --> 00:19:17.550
- This is the aftermath

00:19:17.550 --> 00:19:19.440
of a large scale police raid on a favelas

00:19:21.285 --> 00:19:24.690
Most of the victims are
accused of being gang members.

00:19:24.690 --> 00:19:27.840
Police say they robbed banks, stole cars,

00:19:27.840 --> 00:19:30.007
and were planning attacks.

00:31:35.080 --> 00:31:37.510
- As much as the PCC is a Robin Hood

00:31:37.510 --> 00:31:40.660
to some, they are brutal
and violent to others.

00:31:41.530 --> 00:31:45.947
But as the events have shown,
no one can control them.

